            "body": "Hi [~epayne],\r\n\r\nSorry for the late answer. I unassigned this from myself, but I'd be happy to help reviewing the patch if you have any.\r\n\r\nFor our internal use case it was enough to detect these large aggregated log files. That was implemented in YARN-8199, therefore I did not feel strong push for this feature from our side.",
